SYNOPSIS — PETROCHEMICALS is a ward that has been running about from 1950, but this industry rose long before. It has grown up due to the first and the second world wars. Basic petrochemicals and their derivatives. A history of the petrochemicals development in Brazil, where the production is increasing continuously, but is not yet sufficient for the market requirements.
(Palestra pronunciada em Janeiro de 1965.)
